{"tid":1974311,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑買到水貨ps4手制（求指引）","createTime":"2020-04-15T18:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T09:05:59.000Z","uid":187813,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"2c77605558351581345eaf63257565a0084c025f","tid":1974311,"uid":187813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T18:10:09.000Z","msg":"小弟話說貪平係黃金買咗個ps4手制（已知死，勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），店主聲稱原裝行貨，返到屋企發現鬼鬼地<br />\n<br />\n首先個盒已經奇奇怪怪，原裝個盒（右手邊）有個label係sony一年保養，水貨個盒成個盒身都冇，仲要係韓文字。<br />\n<br />\n第二，原裝個盒有曬說明書，水貨個盒乜都冇。<br />\n<br />\n手制方面，水貨（白色）做工極差，Ext個字斜曬，中間接駁位極不平滑，啲制㩒落都冇咁順，拎上手仲好似比起原廠輕，電量都差啲。<br />\n<br />\n想問下巴打們意見係咪買咗假貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，打算去覆桌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fBwjOim.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfBwjOim.png&h=b7db24c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mzp5JRJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMzp5JRJ.png&h=4edd67d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xmxfmDq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxmxfmDq.png&h=e5704c21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FFvwEqg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFFvwEqg.png&h=d53b9f43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44d64c0ef96660075fc4810ebdcfc699e8ab0bcf","tid":1974311,"uid":187813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T18:34:19.000Z","msg":"最近買咗原廠手掣嘅巴打，可唔可以幫手send個盒既圖上嚟，方便到時對質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7d4d652eaaa5b6010c7d483403e3836a74a814","tid":1974311,"uid":249293,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T18:38:55.000Z","msg":"最近度度都無哂手掣 你買到真係好好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f75466e49c305fa0382eea934130a86adb7f59","tid":1974311,"uid":9729,"like":0,"disl